ToolStripItem.ToolStripItemAccessibleObject Class

Definition

Provides information that accessibility applications use to adjust the user interface of a ToolStripItem for users with impairments.

In this Article

[System.Runtime.InteropServices.ComVisible(true)]
public class ToolStripItem.ToolStripItemAccessibleObject : System.Windows.Forms.AccessibleObject
